          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "It has been four years since our family relocated from abroad and enrolled our children at Pallikkoodam. From the very beginning, the school's friendly and welcoming environment made our children feel at ease, and they quickly adapted to their new surroundings. This journey has been nothing short of wonderful. Over the years, we have witnessed the school's commitment not only to academic excellence but also to providing students with opportunities to express their learning in creative and meaningful ways. Our children have thrived in an atmosphere where they learn joyfully, without pressure, and where the innovative methods used to impart the curriculum ensure that their learning is both lasting and deeply engaging.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Rak's Pallikkoodam - Singanallur"
          },
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Shanmuga Priya"
          },
          "datePublished": "2025-01-11",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As a parent, I am completely satisfied with the experience at Raks.This is 4th year for my son and he enjoys coming to school everyday.The child friendly environment for kids at RAKS, the encouragement to involve the parent community, the various platforms given to the children to have experiential learning - a special mention of the STUDENT LED CONFERENCE by the school.It was amazing to see how kids from Grade 1 and above get to showcase their learning in the most confident and fun way.\n\nRecently, the Year End Programme was remarkable to see our kids to revisit all our old English classics.This shows the versatility of the school in all areas.Iam happy with how school is shaping my son.\n\nIam a proud RAKS parent.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
            "@type": "School",
            "name": "Rak's Pallikkoodam - Singanallur"
          },
          "author": {
