            "name": "Sindhiya Gunasegaran"
          },
          "datePublished": "2025-01-09",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "We clearly said we need admission for IGCSE the admission staff called us and confirmed the board of study that time also I said IGCSE. After going there the staff is saying very lethargic way no admissions are opened up for IGCSE as of now it's all over by October. She could said this before itself we would not wasted our time travelling to their campus. She is saying you could opt for CBSE. Who the hell is she to make us put in other board. If you have no openings for IGCSE you could have informed this earlier so that we would have planned accordingly. Who are you to say put your kid in CBSE? DID I CAME FOR THAT? On doubt only we asked for cambridge books. 1000 rs scam in a simple way. Thank God for showing their darker side.",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "itemReviewed": {
