            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Worst admission staff ever. Getting Admission fee for Igsce and on going there the staff is saying no openings for igcse. They could have said this before itself. No campus visit was allowed. Staff was not ready to explain anything.  Also for the next time we come for admission we have to pay another 1000rs. They are mainly concentrate to get admission to CBSE.\nWorst management. Belive me we enquire about the education system in pallikoodam not up to  the mark in  IGCSE.\nBecause they scare to share the Cambridge assessment and how they Teaching methods in IGCSE.\nThey only focusing to get filling seat in CBSE",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
